You can go first after you freshen up.

56
00:03:06,680 --> 00:03:08,360
I can clean this up by myself.

57
00:03:08,630 --> 00:03:10,170
I'll go there when I'm done.

58
00:03:10,730 --> 00:03:11,570
Really?

59
00:03:11,960 --> 00:03:12,800
That's great.

60
